    "body": "@Kikobeats Thanks for your issue. It goes beyond the scope that we currently envision for instantsearch (react or vanilla). That being said, it's true that the records could contain all the necessary informations to be able to display a detail page. I think we should sync up on the topic with the core team but that's definitely an interesting direction. I think we'll have a first idea on what we're gonna do on that topic next week :)",
